A barefoot bearded man with long flowing hair stands at a wooden podium in a university lecture hall, his arms raised passionately mid-speech, rendered in warm Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures. The audience of diverse students sits captivated in tiered seating, dappled sunlight streaming through tall windows casting golden rectangles across the room. Behind the speaker, an ethereal visualization floats: four glowing birds breaking free from an ornate birdcage, each trailing streams of luminous code that dissolve into cherry blossom petals. The speaker's bare feet are grounded on polished wood floors, his wild appearance contrasting with the refined academic setting. The color palette features warm ambers, soft greens, and gentle blues typical of Miyazaki films, with that distinctive hand-painted quality and attention to atmospheric lighting.
